  • Packages that use com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.reporting 
    Package Description
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.core
    Core library of the autopia4j framework for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.impl.modular
    Core library of the autopia4j modular implementation for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.impl.simple
    Core library of the autopia4j simple implementation for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.mobile
    Mobile device handling library of the autopia4j framework for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing mobile web applications, and integrates with Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.utils
    Utility library of the autopia4j framework for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
